You are implementing Task 2: oa-core — 改造 MailController::sendDecr

## Task Description

**Files:**
- Modify: `oa-core/app/Http/Controllers/MailController.php`
- Modify: `oa-core/config/my_master_api.php`

### What to do:

1. In `MailController.php`, modify the `sendDecr` method to support optional AI analysis. After decryption and before creating BlankMail, check for `ai_analysis_config` parameter and call AiAnalysisService if present.

2. In `config/my_master_api.php`, add `ai_analysis_config` as an optional parameter to the `mail/send-decr` route.

### Current MailController.php content (the full file):

```php
<?php

namespace App\Http\Controllers;

use App\Mail\BlankMail;
use App\Services\AuthorizeService;
use App\Services\DecryptService;
use App\Services\FileService;
use Illuminate\Http\JsonResponse;
use Illuminate\Http\Request;
use Illuminate\Support\Facades\Mail;
use Symfony\Component\Mime\Header\Headers;

/**
 * @codeCoverageIgnore
 */
class MailController extends Controller
{
    public function send(Request $request): JsonResponse
    {
        Headers::$customLineLength = 512;
        $input = $request->all(['content', 'subject', 'to_email']);
        $mail = new BlankMail($input['content']);
        $mail->subject($input['subject']);
        $mail->to($input['to_email']);
        Mail::send($mail);
        return $this->responseJsonSuccess(['success' => true]);
    }

    public function sendDecr(Request $request): JsonResponse
    {
        Headers::$customLineLength = 512;
        $params = $request->all();
        $conf = $params['decrypt_config'];
        unset($params['decrypt_config']);

        [$rcvEmails, $receivers] = AuthorizeService::app()->retrieveEmailsOfReceivers($params['receivers']);
        unset($params['receivers']);

        $conf['receivers'] = $receivers;
        $params = DecryptService::app()->throwEcp()->decryptData($params, $conf, 'send_email');

        $mail = new BlankMail($params['content']);
        $mail->subject($params['subject']);
        $mail->to($rcvEmails);

        if (!empty($params['attachments'])) {
            foreach ($params['attachments'] as $one) {
                $filePath = FileService::app()->getRealFile($one['path'], $one['disk']);
                $realName = $one['real_name'] ?? $one['path'];
                $mail->attach($filePath, [
                    'as' => '=?UTF-8?B?'.base64_encode($realName).'?=',
                ]);
            }
        }

        Mail::send($mail);
        return $this->responseJsonSuccess(['success' => true]);
    }
}
```

### Current my_master_api.php sendDecr route (lines 15-24):

```php
'mail/send-decr' => [
    'params' => [
        'decrypt_config' => 'required|array',
        'receivers' => 'required|array',
        'subject' => 'required|string',
        'content' => 'required|string',
        'attachments' => 'filled|array',
    ],
    'route' => [MailController::class, 'sendDecr'],
],
```

### Changes needed:

**MailController.php sendDecr method:**
1. Add `use App\Services\AiAnalysisService;` at the top
2. After `unset($params['decrypt_config']);`, extract and unset `ai_analysis_config`:
   ```php
   $aiAnalysisConfig = $params['ai_analysis_config'] ?? null;
   unset($params['ai_analysis_config']);
   ```
3. After decryption (`$params = DecryptService::app()->...`), before creating BlankMail, add:
   ```php
   if (!empty($aiAnalysisConfig) && !empty($aiAnalysisConfig['system_prompt'])) {
       $aiResult = AiAnalysisService::app()->analyze(
           $params['content'],
           $aiAnalysisConfig['system_prompt']
       );
       if (!empty($aiResult)) {
           $params['content'] = '<div style="background:#f0f7ff;padding:16px;border-radius:8px;margin-bottom:20px;">'
               . '<h3 style="margin:0 0 12px 0;">📊 AI 分析摘要</h3>'
               . '<div>' . nl2br(e($aiResult)) . '</div>'
               . '</div>'
               . '<hr style="margin:20px 0;">'
               . $params['content'];
       }
   }
   ```

**my_master_api.php:**
Add to the params array:
```php
'ai_analysis_config' => 'nullable|array',
'ai_analysis_config.system_prompt' => 'filled|string',
```

## Context

This is Task 2 in the Smart Daily Report Email System. AiAnalysisService was created in Task 1 and is at `app/Services/AiAnalysisService.php`. The project is a Laravel 9, PHP 8.1 app at D:\project\info-gitlab\oa\oa-core.

## Your Job

1. Read the existing files first
2. Make the modifications described above
3. Do NOT commit
4. Self-review and report back

